com.ucsf.data

Class PatientProfile.Room

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ucsf.core.data.Mote
      • com.ucsf.data.PatientProfile.Room
  • Enclosing class:
    PatientProfile

    public class PatientProfile.Room
extends Mote
    Room representation. Contains mote identification, room floor, ceiling height and distance from the previous room. If a room value is changed, the user will have to redo the beacons test process.
